      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>To render displacement on your geometry in RenderMan for Blender, use the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661545/PxrDisplace\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661545\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrDisplace</a> node.</p><h2 id=\"DisplacementinBlender-AddingPxrDisplace\">Adding PxrDisplace</h2><p /><p>To add PxrDisplace, make sure you've already added a RenderMan material to your geometry. In the material properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"22\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638447\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"material_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4b58f4a7-54c1-4658-8a64-8a4f37b3c8a5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/material_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=23&amp;height=22 1x\"></span> , under the Displacement panel, select PxrDisplace from dropdown list next to &quot;Displacement&quot;.</p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"displacement_pxrdisplace.png\" width=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/displacement_pxrdisplace.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=413&amp;height=73\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/displacement_pxrdisplace.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"73\" data-width=\"413\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638444\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"displacement_pxrdisplace.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"af7dd030-9748-4b57-8d56-244c921e0049\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/displacement_pxrdisplace.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=413&amp;height=73 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/displacement_pxrdisplace.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=413&amp;height=73 1x\"></span><p /><p>The main parameters you will probably be working with are:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Gain</strong>: <span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Gain for the displacement. If it is zero, there will be no displacement. </span></p></li><li><p><strong>Scalar Displacement</strong>: <span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Scalar displacement input. This is a float displacement.</span></p></li><li><p><strong>Vector Displacement</strong>: <span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Vector displacement input. Vector displacement data is a three channel data file,  XYZ.</span></p></li></ul><p>There are also some utility patterns for displacement:</p><ul><li><p>For transform related functions use the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661615/PxrDispTransform\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661615\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrDispTransform</a> pattern. </p></li><li><p>For displacement layering, use either <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661613/PxrDispScalarLayer\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661613\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrDispScalarLayer</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662123/PxrDispVectorLayer\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19662123\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">PxrDispVectorLayer</a> pattern. </p></li></ul><h2 id=\"DisplacementinBlender-Avoidingcracksonpolygonalmeshes\">Avoiding cracks on polygonal meshes</h2><p /><p>When displacing a mesh with hard normals, faces can separate and create cracks. Displacement moves vertices in the direction of its normal but adjacent vertices on different sides of a hard edge have different normals and will move is different directions, creating gaps or cracks.</p><p>RenderMan has a &quot;<code>polygon:smoothdisplacement</code>&quot; attribute that will create a fully smoothed copy of the normals and use it instead of the original normals.</p><p>In RenderMan for Blender, this attribute is enabled by the &quot;Prevent polygon cracking&quot; check box in the object data properties <span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"30\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/object_data_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=29&amp;height=30\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/object_data_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638450\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"object_data_properties.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1eaee564-e108-439a-ba47-42ebe636dd4c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/object_data_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=29&amp;height=30 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/object_data_properties.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703837&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=29&amp;height=30 1x\"></span> on the mesh. </p><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"prevent_polygon_cracks.png\" width=\"683\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/prevent_polygon_cracks.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703596&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=105\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/prevent_polygon_cracks.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703596&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"105\" data-width=\"409\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638441\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"prevent_polygon_cracks.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"78edbbbc-bcd1-4c93-81d5-261af83c1a39\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/prevent_polygon_cracks.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703596&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=105 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/prevent_polygon_cracks.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703596&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=409&amp;height=105 1x\"></span><p /><p>Here's a before and after with displacement attached to a cube mesh.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrdisplace_before.jpg\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/pxrdisplace_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638438\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrdisplace_before.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7e3465fe-8569-472a-8faa-52631eed5534\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_before.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrdisplace_after.jpg\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544638415/pxrdisplace_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"540\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544638435\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrdisplace_after.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544638415\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"23acd254-d549-469c-b8d9-4b7c59f2254d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=540 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544638415/pxrdisplace_after.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432703595&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"354f0fdf-5cf4-4d89-9470-49b89684e17b\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>&quot;Prevent polygon cracking&quot; should only be enabled when necessary as it uses a bit more memory. The amount used is proportional to the number of vertices in the mesh.</p></div></div><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
